						</div>
						<div>
							<h5 class="mb-2 mb-lg-3 fw-bold">Department Of Transport</h5>
							<p>Navigate with ease by renewing your driver’s license.</p>
							<a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" asp-page="/Traffic/Index">Log In</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<div class="d-flex">
						<div class="text-primary me-4">
							<svg class="bi bi-layout-text-window-reverse" fill="currentColor" height="32" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
